  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Laserboy VR is a fast-paced, retro-inspired VR arcade shooter</strong> where precision, speed, and style collide. Wield dual laser weapons, slow down time, and blast through waves of enemies inside visually striking neon arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With intuitive controls, satisfying combat, and multiple ways to customize your playstyle, <strong>Laserboy VR delivers an exhilarating experience for both VR newcomers and high-score hunters.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wield Powerful Laser Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/21f44b1381eb580bb9aa06021316520e.poster.avif?t=1765137615\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/21f44b1381eb580bb9aa06021316520e.webm?t=1765137615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/21f44b1381eb580bb9aa06021316520e.mp4?t=1765137615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dual-wield high-tech laser blasters and slice through enemies with style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slow-Down Time</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the game by slowing down time!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Power-Ups</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Super Shot</strong> – Boosted firepower</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Shield</strong> – 360° protective barrier</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Quad Shot</strong> – Four synchronized laser beams</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle waves of enemies </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UFO's</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drones</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Coins & Upgrade Your Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use coins to improve:<br>• Total HP<br>• Ability strength</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Laser Colors</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new beam colors to personalize your style.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive as the arena ramps up into pure chaos?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore and Fight Across Multiple Arenas</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face enemies in a variety of visually immersive  arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/add49d17cdbbd2b2b4052f53741c5449.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/add49d17cdbbd2b2b4052f53741c5449.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/1b506796852c8269ef657fb709127af2.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/1b506796852c8269ef657fb709127af2.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=530 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/f9dbdea0eaf3291aca7c6ce921201200.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/f9dbdea0eaf3291aca7c6ce921201200.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=428 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/8eb7e7037b0550c78868721499a31c6f.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/8eb7e7037b0550c78868721499a31c6f.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=442 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Laserboy VR is a fast-paced, retro-inspired VR arcade shooter</strong> where precision, speed, and style collide. Wield dual laser weapons, slow down time, and blast through waves of enemies inside visually striking neon arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With intuitive controls, satisfying combat, and multiple ways to customize your playstyle, <strong>Laserboy VR delivers an exhilarating experience for both VR newcomers and high-score hunters.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wield Powerful Laser Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/21f44b1381eb580bb9aa06021316520e.poster.avif?t=1765137615\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/21f44b1381eb580bb9aa06021316520e.webm?t=1765137615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/21f44b1381eb580bb9aa06021316520e.mp4?t=1765137615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dual-wield high-tech laser blasters and slice through enemies with style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slow-Down Time</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the game by slowing down time!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Power-Ups</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Super Shot</strong> – Boosted firepower</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Shield</strong> – 360° protective barrier</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Quad Shot</strong> – Four synchronized laser beams</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle waves of enemies </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UFO's</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drones</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Coins & Upgrade Your Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use coins to improve:<br>• Total HP<br>• Ability strength</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Laser Colors</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new beam colors to personalize your style.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive as the arena ramps up into pure chaos?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore and Fight Across Multiple Arenas</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face enemies in a variety of visually immersive  arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/add49d17cdbbd2b2b4052f53741c5449.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/add49d17cdbbd2b2b4052f53741c5449.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/1b506796852c8269ef657fb709127af2.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/1b506796852c8269ef657fb709127af2.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=530 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras/f9dbdea0eaf3291aca7c6ce921201200.avif?t=1765137615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379190/extras_big/f9dbdea0eaf3291aca7c6ce921201200.avif?t=1765137615 width=800 height=428 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap